Covid Tracking Project US
resource.description:
Data pulled from the the COVID Tracking Project via API displaying information related to COVID-19 testing in the United States. Website found here: https://covidtracking.com

More on the COVID Tracking Project software:

COVID Tracking, developed by Zach Lipton, Josh Ellington, and Ken Riley.
This project uses URL Watch to notify us when a state publishes new numbers.

COVID Tracking API, developed by Kai Curry.
This project uses Cloudflare Workers to expose our data as JSON over HTTP. If you'd like to include our data in your visualization, take a look at this project!

COVID-19 Crawler, developed by Danny Yang.
This project uses Ruby to crawl state websites and update data regularly at Coronavirus (COVID-19) Testing Data. We compare our manually curated data to this data to be sure our numbers look right.
